<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>18 Worlds — A Pokémon Type Atlas</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Nunito:wght@400;600;800;900&family=Bebas+Neue&family=Raleway:wght@300;400;700;900&family=Merriweather:wght@300;400;700&family=Share+Tech+Mono&family=Quicksand:wght@400;600;700&family=Oswald:wght@400;600;700&family=Cinzel:wght@400;700;900&family=Rye&family=Comfortaa:wght@400;700&family=Josefin+Sans:wght@300;400;700&family=Exo+2:wght@400;700;900&family=Permanent+Marker&family=Creepster&family=Cinzel+Decorative:wght@400;700&family=Courier+Prime:wght@400;700&family=Audiowide&family=Pacifico&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
/* ===== RESET & BASE ===== */
*, *::before, *::after { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
body {
  background: #0a0a0f;
  color: #fff;
  font-family: 'Nunito', sans-serif;
  overflow-x: hidden;
  cursor: none;
}
::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 4px; }
::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: #111; }
::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: var(--current-color, #fff); border-radius: 2px; }

/* ===== CUSTOM CURSOR ===== */
#cursor-canvas {
  position: fixed;
  top: 0; left: 0;
  width: 100vw; height: 100vh;
  pointer-events: none;
  z-index: 9999;
}
#cursor-dot {
  position: fixed;
  width: 12px; height: 12px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: #fff;
  pointer-events: none;
  z-index: 10000;
  transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
  transition: background 0.4s ease, box-shadow 0.4s ease;
  mix-blend-mode: screen;
}
#cursor-ring {
  position: fixed;
  width: 40px; height: 40px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  border: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
  pointer-events: none;
  z-index: 9998;
  transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
  transition: border-color 0.4s ease, width 0.2s, height 0.2s;
}

/* ===== SIDEBAR ===== */
#sidebar {
  position: fixed;
  left: 0; top: 0;
  height: 100vh;
  width: 260px;
  background: rgba(5,5,10,0.92);
  backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
  border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
  z-index: 1000;
  transform: translateX(-220px);
  transition: transform 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.46, 0.45, 0.94);
  overflow-y: auto;
  scrollbar-width: none;
}
#sidebar::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }
#sidebar:hover, #sidebar.open { transform: translateX(0); }
#sidebar-toggle {
  position: absolute;
  right: -40px; top: 50%;
  transform: translateY(-50%);
  width: 40px; height: 80px;
  background: rgba(5,5,10,0.9);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
  border-left: none;
  border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  cursor: none;
  writing-mode: vertical-rl;
  font-size: 9px;
  letter-spacing: 3px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
  font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
}
.sidebar-header {
  padding: 32px 20px 20px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
}
.sidebar-header h2 {
  font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
  font-size: 22px;
  letter-spacing: 3px;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
}
.sidebar-header p {
  font-size: 10px;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
  letter-spacing: 1px;
  margin-top: 4px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
}
.sidebar-list { padding: 12px 0; }
.sidebar-item {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 12px;
  padding: 10px 20px;
  cursor: none;
  transition: background 0.2s;
  text-decoration: none;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
  font-size: 13px;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  position: relative;
}
.sidebar-item:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06); color: #fff; }
.sidebar-item.active { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); color: #fff; }
.sidebar-item.active::left-border {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  left: 0; top: 0; bottom: 0;
  width: 3px;
  background: var(--type-color);
}
.type-dot {
  width: 10px; height: 10px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  flex-shrink: 0;
  box-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--dot-color);
}
.sidebar-item.active .type-dot {
  box-shadow: 0 0 14px var(--dot-color), 0 0 4px var(--dot-color);
}
.type-badge-mini {
  margin-left: auto;
  font-size: 9px;
  letter-spacing: 1px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  padding: 2px 8px;
  border-radius: 20px;
  font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
  opacity: 0.7;
}

/* ===== SECTIONS ===== */
section {
  min-height: 100vh;
  position: relative;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  overflow: hidden;
}

/* ===== HERO / LANDING ===== */
#landing {
  background: #050508;
  flex-direction: column;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
  text-align: center;
  min-height: 100vh;
}
.landing-bg {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, #1a0a2e 0%, #05050a 60%);
}
.stars-canvas {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  opacity: 0.6;
}
.landing-content {
  position: relative;
  z-index: 2;
  padding: 20px;
}
.landing-eyebrow {
  font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 11px;
  letter-spacing: 6px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
  margin-bottom: 24px;
  animation: fadeUp 1s ease 0.2s both;
}
.landing-title {
  font-family: 'Cinzel Decorative', serif;
  font-size: clamp(48px, 8vw, 110px);
  font-weight: 700;
  line-height: 0.95;
  margin-bottom: 24px;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff 0%, #a78bfa 40%, #f472b6 70%, #fff 100%);
  -webkit-background-clip: text;
  -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  background-clip: text;
  animation: fadeUp 1s ease 0.4s both;
}
.landing-subtitle {
  font-size: 18px;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
  max-width: 500px;
  line-height: 1.7;
  font-family: 'Raleway', sans-serif;
  font-weight: 300;
  margin: 0 auto 48px;
  animation: fadeUp 1s ease 0.6s both;
}
.type-orbs {
  display: flex;
  gap: 8px;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  justify-content: center;
  max-width: 400px;
  margin: 0 auto 48px;
  animation: fadeUp 1s ease 0.8s both;
}
.type-orb {
  width: 36px; height: 36px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  cursor: none;
  transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
  animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite;
}
.type-orb:hover {
  transform: scale(1.3);
  box-shadow: 0 0 20px currentColor;
}
.scroll-hint {
  font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 11px;
  letter-spacing: 4px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
  animation: fadeUp 1s ease 1s both, pulse 2s ease-in-out 2s infinite;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 12px;
}
.scroll-arrow {
  width: 20px; height: 30px;
  border: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
  border-radius: 10px;
  position: relative;
}
.scroll-arrow::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: 5px; left: 50%;
  transform: translateX(-50%);
  width: 3px; height: 8px;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
  border-radius: 2px;
  animation: scrollDot 1.5s ease-in-out infinite;
}

/* ===== TYPE SECTION BASE ===== */
.type-section {
  min-height: 100vh;
  position: relative;
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0;
  opacity: 0;
  transform: translateY(30px);
  transition: opacity 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.46, 0.45, 0.94), transform 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.46, 0.45, 0.94);
}
.type-section.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
.type-bg {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  z-index: 0;
}
.type-content {
  position: relative;
  z-index: 2;
  padding: 80px 60px 80px 100px;
}
.type-image-side {
  position: relative;
  z-index: 2;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  height: 100vh;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.pokemon-artwork {
  display: none;
}
.type-number {
  font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
  font-size: 280px;
  position: absolute;
  right: 40px; top: 50%;
  transform: translateY(-50%);
  line-height: 1;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  letter-spacing: -10px;
  pointer-events: none;
  z-index: 1;
  mix-blend-mode: screen;
  text-shadow: 0 0 40px var(--type-glow);
}
.type-label {
  font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 10px;
  letter-spacing: 5px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
  margin-bottom: 12px;
}
.type-name {
  font-size: clamp(52px, 6vw, 88px);
  font-weight: 900;
  line-height: 1;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
  color: var(--type-color);
  text-shadow: 0 0 60px var(--type-glow);
}
.pokemon-name {
  font-size: clamp(18px, 2.5vw, 28px);
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
  margin-bottom: 20px;
  font-weight: 300;
  letter-spacing: 2px;
}
.type-badges {
  display: flex;
  gap: 8px;
  margin-bottom: 32px;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}
.type-badge {
  padding: 5px 16px;
  border-radius: 30px;
  font-size: 11px;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 2px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
  backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
}
.type-description {
  font-size: 14px;
  line-height: 1.8;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
  margin-bottom: 24px;
  max-width: 440px;
}
.pokedex-entry {
  background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
  border-left: 3px solid var(--type-color);
  padding: 16px 20px;
  border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
  margin-bottom: 28px;
  max-width: 440px;
}
.pokedex-entry .label {
  font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 9px;
  letter-spacing: 3px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--type-color);
  margin-bottom: 8px;
  opacity: 0.8;
}
.pokedex-entry p {
  font-size: 13px;
  line-height: 1.7;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
  font-style: italic;
}
.type-effectiveness {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 12px;
  max-width: 440px;
}
.effectiveness-box {
  background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
  border-radius: 8px;
  padding: 12px;
}
.effectiveness-box .eff-label {
  font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 8px;
  letter-spacing: 2px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
  opacity: 0.6;
}
.eff-label.strong { color: #4ade80; }
.eff-label.weak { color: #f87171; }
.eff-label.resist { color: #60a5fa; }
.effectiveness-box .eff-types {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 4px;
}
.eff-type-tag {
  font-size: 9px;
  padding: 2px 7px;
  border-radius: 20px;
  font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
  letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
  white-space: nowrap;
}

/* ===== OUTRO ===== */
#outro {
  min-height: 60vh;
  background: #050508;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  text-align: center;
  padding: 80px 20px;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.outro-content {
  position: relative;
  z-index: 2;
}
.outro-title {
  font-family: 'Cinzel Decorative', serif;
  font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 56px);
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}
.outro-text {
  font-size: 16px;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
  max-width: 500px;
  line-height: 1.8;
  font-family: 'Raleway', sans-serif;
  margin-bottom: 40px;
}
.outro-orbs {
  display: flex;
  gap: 16px;
  justify-content: center;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}
.outro-orb {
  width: 16px; height: 16px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite;
}
.outro-credit {
  margin-top: 60px;
  font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 10px;
  letter-spacing: 3px;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
  text-transform: uppercase;
}

/* ===== ANIMATIONS ===== */
@keyframes fadeUp {
  from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); }
  to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
}
@keyframes float {
  0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
  50% { transform: translateY(-16px); }
}
@keyframes pulse {
  0%, 100% { opacity: 0.3; }
  50% { opacity: 0.7; }
}
@keyframes scrollDot {
  0% { transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(0); opacity: 1; }
  100% { transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(12px); opacity: 0; }
}
@keyframes flicker {
  0%, 100% { opacity: 1; } 50% { opacity: 0.7; }
}

/* ===== TYPE-SPECIFIC BACKGROUNDS — Nano Banana 2 integrated scenes ===== */
/* Pattern: each section has a full-bleed generated scene with the Pokémon already in it.
   A gradient overlay (::before) fades from dark on the content side (for text legibility)
   to transparent on the scene side (where the Pokémon is visible). */

.type-bg { background-size: cover; background-position: center; }
.type-bg::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  z-index: 1;
}

/* NORMAL — Eevee in sunlit meadow (content LEFT → fade to right) */
.bg-normal { background: url('./images/normal.jpg') center/cover no-repeat, #12110c; }
.bg-normal::before {
  background:
    linear-gradient(to right, rgba(18,17,12,0.92) 0%, rgba(18,17,12,0.55) 45%, rgba(18,17,12,0.1) 100%),
    radial-gradient(ellipse at 70% 50%, rgba(168,167,122,0.18) 0%, transparent 65%);
  animation: softBreath 6s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
}

/* FIRE — Charizard breathing fire (content RIGHT → fade to left) */
.bg-fire { background: url('./images/fire.jpg') center/cover no-repeat, #0a0200; }
.bg-fire::before {
  background:
    linear-gradient(to left, rgba(10,2,0,0.92) 0%, rgba(10,2,0,0.5) 45%, rgba(10,2,0,0.1) 100%),
    radial-gradient(ellipse at 30% 60%, rgba(238,100,0,0.28) 0%, transparent 65%);
  animation: fireFlicker 2.8s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
}
@keyframes fireFlicker {
  from { opacity: 0.7; }
  to { opacity: 1; }
}

/* WATER — Blastoise firing hydro cannons (content LEFT → fade to right) */
.bg-water { background: url('./images/water.jpg') center/cover no-repeat, #020d1a; }
.bg-water::before {
  background:
    linear-gradient(to right, rgba(2,13,26,0.92) 0%, rgba(2,13,26,0.5) 45%, rgba(2,13,26,0.1) 100%),
    radial-gradient(ellipse at 70% 50%, rgba(99,144,240,0.22) 0%, transparent 65%);
  animation: waveShimmer 4.5s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
}
@keyframes waveShimmer {
  from { opacity: 0.7; }
  to { opacity: 1; }
}

/* GRASS — Venusaur releasing spores (content RIGHT → fade to left) */
.bg-grass { background: url('./images/grass.jpg') center/cover no-repeat, #031005; }
.bg-grass::before {
  background:
    linear-gradient(to left, rgba(3,16,5,0.92) 0%, rgba(3,16,5,0.5) 45%, rgba(3,16,5,0.1) 100%),
    radial-gradient(ellipse at 30% 60%, rgba(122,199,76,0.22) 0%, transparent 65%);
  animation: grassBreath 5s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
}
@keyframes grassBreath {
  from { opacity: 0.75; }
  to { opacity: 1; }
}

/* ELECTRIC — Pikachu unleashing thunderbolt (content LEFT → fade to right) */
.bg-electric { background: url('./images/electric.jpg') center/cover no-repeat, #0a0900; }
.bg-electric::before {
  background:
    linear-gradient(to right, rgba(10,9,0,0.88) 0%, rgba(10,9,0,0.45) 45%, rgba(10,9,0,0.1) 100%),
    radial-gradient(ellipse at 70% 40%, rgba(247,208,44,0.22) 0%, transparent 65%);
  animation: electricPulse 1.5s ease-in-out infinite;
}
@keyframes electricPulse {
  0%, 100% { opacity: 0.55; }
  50% { opacity: 1; }
}

/* ICE — Articuno soaring over tundra (content RIGHT → fade to left) */
.bg-ice { background: url('./images/ice.jpg') center/cover no-repeat, #040c0d; }
.bg-ice::before {
  background:
    linear-gradient(to left, rgba(4,12,13,0.92) 0%, rgba(4,12,13,0.5) 45%, rgba(4,12,13,0.1) 100%),
    radial-gradient(ellipse at 30% 50%, rgba(150,217,214,0.2) 0%, transparent 65%);
  animation: iceShimmer 5s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
}
@keyframes iceShimmer {
  from { opacity: 0.75; }
  to { opacity: 1; }
}

/* FIGHTING — Lucario smashing rocks (content LEFT → fade to right) */
.bg-fighting { background: url('./images/fighting.jpg') center/cover no-repeat, #0a0202; }
.bg-fighting::before {
  background:
    linear-gradient(to right, rgba(10,2,2,0.92) 0%, rgba(10,2,2,0.5) 45%, rgba(10,2,2,0.1) 100%),
    radial-gradient(ellipse at 70% 55%, rgba(194,46,40,0.22) 0%, transparent 65%);
  animation: auraPulse 2.5s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
}
@keyframes auraPulse {
  from { opacity: 0.75; }
  to { opacity: 1; }
}

/* POISON — Nidoking roaring toxic gas (content RIGHT → fade to left) */
.bg-poison { background: url('./images/poison.jpg') center/cover no-repeat, #0b000c; }
.bg-poison::before {
  background:
    linear-gradient(to left, rgba(11,0,12,0.92) 0%, rgba(11,0,12,0.5) 45%, rgba(11,0,12,0.1) 100%),
    radial-gradient(ellipse at 30% 55%, rgba(163,62,161,0.28) 0%, transparent 65%);
  animation: poisonBubble 3s ease-in-out infinite;
}
@keyframes poisonBubble {
  0%, 100% { opacity: 0.6; }
  50% { opacity: 1; }
}

/* GROUND — Garchomp erupting from sand (content LEFT → fade to right) */
.bg-ground { background: url('./images/ground.jpg') center/cover no-repeat, #0f0a00; }
.bg-ground::before {
  background:
    linear-gradient(to right, rgba(15,10,0,0.92) 0%, rgba(15,10,0,0.5) 45%, rgba(15,10,0,0.1) 100%),
    radial-gradient(ellipse at 70% 60%, rgba(226,191,101,0.22) 0%, transparent 65%);
  animation: sandShift 5s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
}
@keyframes sandShift {
  from { opacity: 0.7; }
  to { opacity: 1; }
}

/* FLYING — Staraptor diving through clouds (content RIGHT → fade to left) */
.bg-flying { background: url('./images/flying.jpg') center/cover no-repeat, #05050f; }
.bg-flying::before {
  background:
    linear-gradient(to left, rgba(5,5,15,0.9) 0%, rgba(5,5,15,0.45) 45%, rgba(5,5,15,0.08) 100%),
    radial-gradient(ellipse at 30% 40%, rgba(169,143,243,0.22) 0%, transparent 65%);
  animation: cloudDrift 6s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
}
@keyframes cloudDrift {
  from { opacity: 0.75; }
  to { opacity: 1; }
}

/* PSYCHIC — Alakazam warping reality (content LEFT → fade to right) */
.bg-psychic { background: url('./images/psychic.jpg') center/cover no-repeat, #0a0008; }
.bg-psychic::before {
  background:
    linear-gradient(to right, rgba(10,0,8,0.92) 0%, rgba(10,0,8,0.5) 45%, rgba(10,0,8,0.1) 100%),
    radial-gradient(ellipse at 70% 50%, rgba(249,85,135,0.22) 0%, transparent 65%);
  animation: psychicPulse 4s ease-in-out infinite;
}
@keyframes psychicPulse {
  0%, 100% { opacity: 0.65; }
  50% { opacity: 1; }
}

/* BUG — Volcarona shedding scales (content RIGHT → fade to left) */
.bg-bug { background: url('./images/bug.jpg') center/cover no-repeat, #060800; }
.bg-bug::before {
  background:
    linear-gradient(to left, rgba(6,8,0,0.92) 0%, rgba(6,8,0,0.5) 45%, rgba(6,8,0,0.1) 100%),
    radial-gradient(ellipse at 30% 45%, rgba(166,185,26,0.22) 0%, transparent 65%);
  animation: emberDance 3s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
}
@keyframes emberDance {
  from { opacity: 0.7; }
  to { opacity: 1; }
}

/* ROCK — Tyranitar summoning sandstorm (content LEFT → fade to right) */
.bg-rock { background: url('./images/rock.jpg') center/cover no-repeat, #0a0800; }
.bg-rock::before {
  background:
    linear-gradient(to right, rgba(10,8,0,0.92) 0%, rgba(10,8,0,0.5) 45%, rgba(10,8,0,0.1) 100%),
    radial-gradient(ellipse at 70% 60%, rgba(182,161,54,0.22) 0%, transparent 65%);
  animation: dustSwirl 5s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
}
@keyframes dustSwirl {
  from { opacity: 0.7; }
  to { opacity: 1; }
}

/* GHOST — Gengar phasing through cathedral (content RIGHT → fade to left) */
.bg-ghost { background: url('./images/ghost.jpg') center/cover no-repeat, #030004; }
.bg-ghost::before {
  background:
    linear-gradient(to left, rgba(3,0,4,0.9) 0%, rgba(3,0,4,0.5) 45%, rgba(3,0,4,0.1) 100%),
    radial-gradient(ellipse at 30% 45%, rgba(115,87,151,0.25) 0%, transparent 65%);
  animation: spectralFloat 6s ease-in-out infinite;
}
@keyframes spectralFloat {
  0%, 100% { opacity: 0.7; }
  50% { opacity: 1; }
}

/* DRAGON — Dragonite flying above clouds (content LEFT → fade to right) */
.bg-dragon { background: url('./images/dragon.jpg') center/cover no-repeat, #04000c; }
.bg-dragon::before {
  background:
    linear-gradient(to right, rgba(4,0,12,0.92) 0%, rgba(4,0,12,0.5) 45%, rgba(4,0,12,0.1) 100%),
    radial-gradient(ellipse at 70% 50%, rgba(111,53,252,0.22) 0%, transparent 65%);
  animation: majestyPulse 5s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
}
@keyframes majestyPulse {
  from { opacity: 0.75; }
  to { opacity: 1; }
}

/* DARK — Umbreon in moonlit forest (content RIGHT → fade to left) */
.bg-dark { background: url('./images/dark.jpg') center/cover no-repeat, #050201; }
.bg-dark::before {
  background:
    linear-gradient(to left, rgba(5,2,1,0.92) 0%, rgba(5,2,1,0.5) 45%, rgba(5,2,1,0.1) 100%),
    radial-gradient(ellipse at 30% 50%, rgba(112,87,70,0.2) 0%, transparent 65%);
  animation: moonBreath 7s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
}
@keyframes moonBreath {
  from { opacity: 0.7; }
  to { opacity: 1; }
}

/* STEEL — Metagross over industrial fortress (content LEFT → fade to right) */
.bg-steel { background: url('./images/steel.jpg') center/cover no-repeat, #0a0a10; }
.bg-steel::before {
  background:
    linear-gradient(to right, rgba(10,10,16,0.92) 0%, rgba(10,10,16,0.5) 45%, rgba(10,10,16,0.1) 100%),
    radial-gradient(ellipse at 70% 45%, rgba(183,183,206,0.2) 0%, transparent 65%);
  animation: steelShimmer 3s linear infinite;
}
@keyframes steelShimmer {
  0% { opacity: 0.55; }
  50% { opacity: 1; }
  100% { opacity: 0.55; }
}

/* FAIRY — Sylveon in enchanted garden (content RIGHT → fade to left) */
.bg-fairy { background: url('./images/fairy.jpg') center/cover no-repeat, #0a0006; }
.bg-fairy::before {
  background:
    linear-gradient(to left, rgba(10,0,6,0.85) 0%, rgba(10,0,6,0.4) 45%, rgba(10,0,6,0.08) 100%),
    radial-gradient(ellipse at 30% 50%, rgba(214,133,173,0.22) 0%, transparent 65%);
  animation: fairySparkle 4s ease-in-out infinite;
}
@keyframes fairySparkle {
  0%, 100% { opacity: 0.65; }
  50% { opacity: 1; }
}

@keyframes softBreath {
  from { opacity: 0.75; }
  to { opacity: 1; }
}

/* ===== PARTICLE LAYERS ===== */
.particle-layer {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  overflow: hidden;
  pointer-events: none;
  z-index: 2;
}
.particle {
  position: absolute;
  border-radius: 50%;
  animation: linear infinite;
  will-change: transform, opacity;
}
.p-ring { background: transparent !important; border: 1.5px solid currentColor; }
.p-leaf { border-radius: 80% 0 80% 0; }
.p-streak { border-radius: 0 !important; }
.p-star {
  background: transparent !important;
  border-radius: 0;
}
.p-star::before, .p-star::after {
  content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0;
  background: currentColor; border-radius: 1px;
}
.p-star::before { transform: rotate(0deg); }
.p-star::after { transform: rotate(45deg); }

/* Rise (fire embers, ghost flames, dragon sparks) */
.p-rise { animation-name: pRise; }
@keyframes pRise {
  0% { transform: translateY(100vh) translateX(0) scale(0.4); opacity: 0; }
  10% { opacity: 1; }
  50% { transform: translateY(50vh) translateX(18px) scale(1); }
  90% { opacity: 0.8; }
  100% { transform: translateY(-120px) translateX(-18px) scale(0.2); opacity: 0; }
}
/* Bubble (water, poison) */
.p-bubble { animation-name: pBubble; animation-timing-function: ease-in-out; }
@keyframes pBubble {
  0% { transform: translateY(105vh) scale(0); opacity: 0; }
  12% { opacity: 0.8; transform: translateY(80vh) scale(1); }
  50% { transform: translateY(40vh) translateX(22px) scale(1.1); }
  90% { opacity: 0.7; }
  100% { transform: translateY(-80px) translateX(-18px) scale(0); opacity: 0; }
}
/* Fall (snow, leaves) */
.p-fall { animation-name: pFall; }
@keyframes pFall {
  0% { transform: translateY(-100px) translateX(0) rotate(0deg); opacity: 0; }
  10% { opacity: 1; }
  50% { transform: translateY(50vh) translateX(35px) rotate(180deg); }
  90% { opacity: 1; }
  100% { transform: translateY(110vh) translateX(-35px) rotate(360deg); opacity: 0; }
}
/* Drift (pollen, dust) */
.p-drift { animation-name: pDrift; }
@keyframes pDrift {
  0% { transform: translateY(100vh) translateX(0); opacity: 0; }
  15% { opacity: 0.7; }
  50% { transform: translateY(50vh) translateX(40px); }
  85% { opacity: 0.7; }
  100% { transform: translateY(-120px) translateX(-40px); opacity: 0; }
}
/* Spark zip (electric, fighting, steel) */
.p-spark { animation-name: pSpark; }
@keyframes pSpark {
  0% { transform: translate(0,0) scale(0); opacity: 0; }
  10% { opacity: 1; transform: translate(0,0) scale(1.2); }
  100% { transform: translate(140px, 100px) scale(0); opacity: 0; }
}
/* Streak (flying wind) */
.p-streak-m { animation-name: pStreak; }
@keyframes pStreak {
  0% { transform: translateX(-200px); opacity: 0; }
  20% { opacity: 0.9; }
  80% { opacity: 0.9; }
  100% { transform: translateX(110vw); opacity: 0; }
}
/* Twinkle (fairy, bug firefly, psychic) */
.p-twinkle { animation-name: pTwinkle; animation-timing-function: ease-in-out; }
@keyframes pTwinkle {
  0%, 100% { transform: scale(0); opacity: 0; }
  50% { transform: scale(1.3); opacity: 1; }
}

/* ===== PER-TYPE FX LAYER — atmosphere details ===== */
.type-fx {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  z-index: 1;
  pointer-events: none;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.type-fx::before, .type-fx::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
}
/* Pause animations on sections not currently near viewport for perf */
.type-section:not(.active-fx) .type-fx::before,
.type-section:not(.active-fx) .type-fx::after,
.type-section:not(.active-fx) .particle {
  animation-play-state: paused;
}

/* NORMAL — soft sun rays */
.fx-normal::before {
  background: radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 70% 15%, rgba(255,220,160,0.18), transparent 55%);
  animation: fxSoftRays 6s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
}
@keyframes fxSoftRays { from { opacity: 0.5; transform: translateY(0); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(-8px); } }

/* FIRE — heat shimmer + ember wave */
.fx-fire::before {
  background:
    linear-gradient(to top, rgba(255,120,40,0.22) 0%, transparent 40%),
    radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 40% at 30% 100%, rgba(255,200,100,0.2), transparent 60%);
  filter: blur(2px);
  animation: fxHeatShimmer 2.6s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
}
.fx-fire::after {
  top: 55%;
  background: repeating-linear-gradient(90deg,
    transparent 0, rgba(255,180,80,0.06) 30px, transparent 60px);
  filter: blur(3px);
  animation: fxHeatWave 3s linear infinite;
}
@keyframes fxHeatShimmer { from { transform: translateY(0) scaleY(1); opacity: 0.7; } to { transform: translateY(-6px) scaleY(1.03); opacity: 1; } }
@keyframes fxHeatWave { from { transform: translateX(0) skewX(0deg); } to { transform: translateX(-120px) skewX(0.5deg); } }

/* WATER — rolling wave bands */
.fx-water::before {
  background: radial-gradient(ellipse 130% 50% at 50% 100%, rgba(99,144,240,0.28) 0%, transparent 65%);
  animation: fxWaveRoll 4.5s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
}
.fx-water::after {
  background: repeating-linear-gradient(0deg,
    transparent 0, rgba(150,200,255,0.05) 3px, transparent 6px);
  animation: fxRipple 3.5s linear infinite;
  mix-blend-mode: overlay;
}
@keyframes fxWaveRoll { from { transform: translateX(-30px) scaleY(1); opacity: 0.7; } to { transform: translateX(30px) scaleY(1.08); opacity: 1; } }
@keyframes fxRipple { from { transform: translateY(0); } to { transform: translateY(24px); } }

/* GRASS — swaying foliage + pollen glow */
.fx-grass::before {
  background:
    radial-gradient(circle at 12% 88%, rgba(80,180,60,0.3), transparent 35%),
    radial-gradient(circle at 88% 92%, rgba(60,150,50,0.25), transparent 30%),
    radial-gradient(circle at 50% 100%, rgba(50,140,60,0.25), transparent 40%);
  animation: fxSway 5s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
}
.fx-grass::after {
  background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 40%, rgba(180,220,120,0.12), transparent 60%);
  animation: fxSporeGlow 4s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
}
@keyframes fxSway { from { transform: translateX(-6px) rotate(-0.4deg); } to { transform: translateX(6px) rotate(0.4deg); } }
@keyframes fxSporeGlow { from { opacity: 0.5; } to { opacity: 1; } }

/* ELECTRIC — lightning flash bursts */
.fx-electric::before {
  background: radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 50% 30%, rgba(255,245,130,0.35), transparent 60%);
  animation: fxFlash 4s ease-out infinite;
}
.fx-electric::after {
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent 30%, rgba(255,255,200,0.08) 50%, transparent 70%);
  background-size: 300% 100%;
  animation: fxStrike 2s linear infinite;
}
@keyframes fxFlash {
  0%, 88%, 92%, 96%, 100% { opacity: 0; }
  90% { opacity: 1; }
  94% { opacity: 0.4; }
}
@keyframes fxStrike { from { background-position: 0 0; } to { background-position: 300% 0; } }

/* ICE — frost edges + slow shimmer */
.fx-ice::before {
  background:
    linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(200,230,250,0.18), transparent 30%),
    linear-gradient(to top, rgba(200,230,250,0.12), transparent 30%);
  animation: fxFrostPulse 4.5s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
}
.fx-ice::after {
  background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 50%, transparent 40%, rgba(180,220,240,0.1) 100%);
  animation: fxAurora 7s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
}
@keyframes fxFrostPulse { from { opacity: 0.5; } to { opacity: 1; } }
@keyframes fxAurora { from { opacity: 0.3; transform: translateX(-10px); } to { opacity: 0.8; transform: translateX(10px); } }

/* FIGHTING — aura shockwave */
.fx-fighting::before {
  background: radial-gradient(circle at 35% 50%, rgba(255,80,60,0.2), transparent 40%);
  animation: fxAuraPulse 2s ease-out infinite;
}
.fx-fighting::after {
  background: radial-gradient(circle at 35% 50%, transparent 20%, rgba(100,180,255,0.1) 22%, transparent 28%);
  animation: fxShock 2.4s ease-out infinite;
}
@keyframes fxAuraPulse { 0% { transform: scale(0.92); opacity: 0.3; } 70% { opacity: 1; } 100% { transform: scale(1.15); opacity: 0; } }
@keyframes fxShock { 0% { transform: scale(0.5); opacity: 0.6; } 100% { transform: scale(2); opacity: 0; } }

/* POISON — bubbling miasma */
.fx-poison::before {
  background:
    radial-gradient(circle at 20% 70%, rgba(163,62,161,0.25), transparent 45%),
    radial-gradient(circle at 80% 30%, rgba(140,220,80,0.18), transparent 40%);
  animation: fxGasSwirl 5s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
}
@keyframes fxGasSwirl { from { transform: translate(-6px,-4px); opacity: 0.6; } to { transform: translate(6px,4px); opacity: 1; } }

/* GROUND — drifting dust cloud */
.fx-ground::before {
  background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(226,191,101,0.18), transparent 40%);
  animation: fxDustBlow 5s linear infinite;
}
.fx-ground::after {
  background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 100%, rgba(180,140,70,0.18), transparent 50%);
  animation: fxQuake 0.3s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
}
@keyframes fxDustBlow { 0% { transform: translateX(-30px); opacity: 0.4; } 50% { opacity: 1; } 100% { transform: translateX(30px); opacity: 0.4; } }
@keyframes fxQuake { from { transform: translateY(0); } to { transform: translateY(1px); } }

/* FLYING — wind streak bands */
.fx-flying::before {
  background: repeating-linear-gradient(-10deg,
    transparent 0, rgba(220,220,255,0.06) 40%, transparent 70%);
  background-size: 200% 100%;
  animation: fxWindStreak 3.5s linear infinite;
}
@keyframes fxWindStreak { from { background-position: 0 0; } to { background-position: 400px 0; } }

/* PSYCHIC — warp pulse + hue rotation */
.fx-psychic::before {
  background: radial-gradient(circle at 50% 50%, rgba(249,85,135,0.2), transparent 60%);
  animation: fxWarpPulse 3.5s ease-in-out infinite;
}
.fx-psychic::after {
  background: conic-gradient(from 0deg at 60% 50%, transparent, rgba(200,100,255,0.08), transparent);
  animation: fxSpin 10s linear infinite;
}
@keyframes fxWarpPulse { 0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); filter: hue-rotate(0); opacity: 0.5; } 50% { transform: scale(1.1); filter: hue-rotate(20deg); opacity: 1; } }
@keyframes fxSpin { from { transform: rotate(0deg); } to { transform: rotate(360deg); } }

/* BUG — firefly glow clusters */
.fx-bug::before {
  background:
    radial-gradient(circle at 30% 40%, rgba(255,200,80,0.18), transparent 30%),
    radial-gradient(circle at 70% 60%, rgba(166,185,26,0.15), transparent 30%);
  animation: fxFireflies 3s ease-in-out infinite;
}
@keyframes fxFireflies { 0%, 100% { opacity: 0.4; } 50% { opacity: 1; } }

/* ROCK — sandstorm sweep */
.fx-rock::before {
  background: linear-gradient(45deg, transparent 30%, rgba(200,160,80,0.18) 50%, transparent 70%);
  background-size: 220% 220%;
  animation: fxSandstorm 5s linear infinite;
}
@keyframes fxSandstorm { from { background-position: 0 0; } to { background-position: 400% 400%; } }

/* GHOST — purple flames flicker */
.fx-ghost::before {
  background:
    radial-gradient(circle at 20% 30%, rgba(180,120,210,0.22), transparent 40%),
    radial-gradient(circle at 80% 70%, rgba(100,50,140,0.22), transparent 40%);
  animation: fxGhostFlicker 3.5s ease-in-out infinite;
}
@keyframes fxGhostFlicker {
  0%, 100% { opacity: 0.5; transform: translateY(0) scale(1); }
  30% { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(-4px) scale(1.02); }
  60% { opacity: 0.7; transform: translateY(2px) scale(0.98); }
}

/* DRAGON — majestic cloud sweep */
.fx-dragon::before {
  background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 70% 50%, rgba(140,80,255,0.2), transparent 55%);
  animation: fxDragonPulse 5s ease-in-out infinite;
}
.fx-dragon::after {
  background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, rgba(200,180,255,0.08), transparent);
  animation: fxCloudSweep 8s linear infinite;
  background-size: 200% 100%;
}
@keyframes fxDragonPulse { 0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 0.6; } 50% { transform: scale(1.08); opacity: 1; } }
@keyframes fxCloudSweep { from { background-position: -200% 0; } to { background-position: 200% 0; } }

/* DARK — moonlight beam + shadow mist */
.fx-dark::before {
  background: radial-gradient(ellipse 50% 60% at 50% 0%, rgba(200,210,230,0.16), transparent 50%);
  animation: fxMoonGlow 6s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
}
.fx-dark::after {
  background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 100%, rgba(20,10,25,0.6), transparent 60%);
  animation: fxShadowMist 5s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
}
@keyframes fxMoonGlow { from { opacity: 0.5; } to { opacity: 1; } }
@keyframes fxShadowMist { from { transform: translateX(-20px); opacity: 0.5; } to { transform: translateX(20px); opacity: 0.9; } }

/* STEEL — chrome shine sweep */
.fx-steel::before {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, transparent 30%, rgba(220,230,255,0.15) 50%, transparent 70%);
  background-size: 250% 250%;
  animation: fxChromeShine 3.5s linear infinite;
}
@keyframes fxChromeShine { from { background-position: 0 0; } to { background-position: 250% 250%; } }

/* FAIRY — floating hearts wash */
.fx-fairy::before {
  background:
    radial-gradient(circle at 30% 30%, rgba(255,180,220,0.2), transparent 35%),
    radial-gradient(circle at 70% 70%, rgba(255,200,230,0.15), transparent 35%);
  animation: fxFairyWash 4s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
}
.fx-fairy::after {
  background: radial-gradient(circle at 50% 50%, rgba(255,220,235,0.1), transparent 60%);
  animation: fxFairyPulse 3s ease-in-out infinite;
}
@keyframes fxFairyWash { from { opacity: 0.6; transform: rotate(-1deg) scale(1); } to { opacity: 1; transform: rotate(1deg) scale(1.02); } }
@keyframes fxFairyPulse { 0%, 100% { opacity: 0.5; } 50% { opacity: 1; } }

/* ===== SECTION DIVIDER — color bleed to next type ===== */
.section-divider {
  position: absolute;
  bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
  height: 180px;
  z-index: 3;
  pointer-events: none;
  background: linear-gradient(to bottom,
    transparent 0%,
    rgba(0,0,0,0.35) 55%,
    rgba(0,0,0,0.7) 100%);
}
.section-divider::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  bottom: -40px; left: 50%;
  transform: translateX(-50%);
  width: 120%; height: 240px;
  background: radial-gradient(ellipse 50% 60% at 50% 100%, var(--next-type-glow, rgba(255,255,255,0.05)) 0%, transparent 70%);
  opacity: 0.75;
  filter: blur(2px);
}
.section-divider::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
  height: 1px;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent 10%, var(--next-type-color, rgba(255,255,255,0.3)) 50%, transparent 90%);
  opacity: 0.6;
  box-shadow: 0 0 24px var(--next-type-color, rgba(255,255,255,0.2));
}

/* ===== RESPONSIVE ===== */
@media (max-width: 900px) {
  .type-section {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    grid-template-rows: auto auto;
  }
  .type-content {
    padding: 60px 24px 40px 60px;
    order: 2;
  }
  .type-image-side {
    height: 40vh;
    order: 1;
  }
  .pokemon-artwork { width: min(260px, 80%); }
  .type-name { font-size: 48px; }
  .type-effectiveness { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
}
@media (max-width: 600px) {
  .type-content { padding: 40px 20px 40px 50px; }
  .type-effectiveness { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  #sidebar { width: 240px; transform: translateX(-200px); }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- CUSTOM CURSOR -->
<canvas id="cursor-canvas"></canvas>
<div id="cursor-dot"></div>
<div id="cursor-ring"></div>

<!-- SIDEBAR -->
<nav id="sidebar" role="navigation" aria-label="Type navigation">
  <div id="sidebar-toggle" aria-hidden="true">TYPES</div>
  <div class="sidebar-header">
    <h2>TYPE ATLAS</h2>
    <p>18 Worlds · All Generations</p>
  </div>
  <div class="sidebar-list" id="sidebar-list"></div>
</nav>

<!-- ===== LANDING ===== -->
<section id="landing">
  <div class="landing-bg"></div>
  <canvas class="stars-canvas" id="stars-canvas"></canvas>
  <div class="landing-content">
    <p class="landing-eyebrow">A Pokémon Type Atlas</p>
    <h1 class="landing-title">18 Worlds</h1>
    <p class="landing-subtitle">Every type is a universe. Step inside each one — from the volcanic fury of Fire to the ethereal silence of Ghost.</p>
    <div class="type-orbs" id="landing-orbs"></div>
    <div class="scroll-hint">
      <div class="scroll-arrow"></div>
      Scroll to explore
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== TYPE SECTIONS (generated by JS) ===== -->
<div id="type-sections-container"></div>

<!-- ===== OUTRO ===== -->
<section id="outro">
  <div class="outro-content">
    <h2 class="outro-title">Every World Explored.</h2>
    <p class="outro-text">From the everyday grace of Normal to the divine magic of Fairy — 18 types, 18 stories, one Pokémon world. This is a non-commercial educational project.</p>
    <div class="outro-orbs" id="outro-orbs"></div>
    <p class="outro-credit">Pokémon © 1995–2025 Nintendo · Game Freak · Creatures Inc. — School Final Project</p>
  </div>
</section>

<script>
// ===== TYPE DATA =====
const TYPES = [
  {
    id: 'normal',
    name: 'NORMAL',
    color: '#A8A77A',
    glow: 'rgba(168,167,122,0.5)',
    shadow: 'rgba(168,167,122,0.4)',
    bg: 'bg-normal',
    font: "'Nunito', sans-serif",
    fontWeight: '800',
    pokemon: 'Eevee',
    pokemonId: 133,
    types: ['Normal'],
    whyBest: 'Eevee is the ultimate Normal-type icon — the only Pokémon with eight distinct evolutions, all triggered by its environment. This genetic flexibility is the very soul of the Normal type: adaptable, full of potential, and deceptively powerful despite its unassuming appearance.',
    typeRole: 'Normal types are the versatile backbone of the Pokémon world. Unspecialized but never weak, they represent everyday life, steady growth, and hidden potential. In battle, they resist nothing and fall only to Fighting — but their moves land neutrally against nearly everything.',
    dex: '"Its genes are easily influenced by its surroundings. Even its face starts to look like that of its Trainer." — Pokémon Ultra Moon',
    strong: ['—'],
    weak: ['Fighting'],
    resist: ['—'],
    immune: ['Ghost'],
    cursorColors: ['#A8A77A', '#d4d0a0', '#e8e6c4'],
    particleColor: 'rgba(168,167,122,0.4)',
  },
  {
    id: 'fire',
    name: 'FIRE',
    color: '#EE8130',
    glow: 'rgba(238,129,48,0.6)',
    shadow: 'rgba(238,80,20,0.6)',
    bg: 'bg-fire',
    font: "'Bebas Neue', sans-serif",
    fontWeight: '400',
    pokemon: 'Charizard',
    pokemonId: 6,
    types: ['Fire', 'Flying'],
    whyBest: 'Charizard is the eternal symbol of fire\'s duality — destruction and majesty intertwined. Its code of honor, refusing to burn weaker opponents, elevates it beyond raw power. It doesn\'t just embody Fire; it commands it with a warrior\'s spirit.',
    typeRole: 'Fire types are forces of pure transformation — consuming the old to forge something new. In battle, they incinerate Grass, Bug, Ice, and Steel, punishing those who stand rigid against the heat. Their greatest foes are Water, Rock, and Ground.',
    dex: '"Charizard flies around the sky in search of powerful opponents. It breathes fire of such great heat that it melts anything. However, it never turns its fiery breath on any opponent weaker than itself." — Generation III',
    strong: ['Bug', 'Grass', 'Ice', 'Steel'],
    weak: ['Water', 'Rock', 'Ground'],
